    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for a solid foundation. The engine and transmission are in good working order, though the car does show its age with some noticeable exterior scratches and minor interior upholstery wear. While it is fully operational, a prospective buyer should expect to address some minor cosmetic issues and perhaps some upcoming routine maintenance to bring it back to its best. It's a great choice for someone who values mechanical reliability over a perfect aesthetic.",
