    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some minor fading in the clear coat, while the interior shows typical wear on the upholstery and carpets. Mechanically, the car starts and runs reliably, but it may require some upcoming maintenance like new brake pads or a suspension tune-up in the near future. It\u2019s a solid option for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind a bit of character and a few minor projects.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
